    dc:description "FIGURES 1–9. Hydatothrips longirostris sp.n. (1) Female; (2) Male; (3) Antenna; (4) Pronotum; (5) Meso and metanotum; (6) Head, dorsal; (7) Fore wing; (8) Mouth cone; (9) Female abdominal tergites IX–X." ;
