<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8221943>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–14. Hydatothrips longirostris sp.n. (10) Abdominal tergite III; (11) Abdominal tergite VII; (12) Pore plate on male abdominal sternites III–VII; (13) Male abdominal tergites IX–X; (14) Abdominal tergite VIII." ;
